title: 364-Your Mom's House with Christina Pazsitzky and Tom Segura
description: This week, the mommies discover and fall in love with a new Dan Pena clip, get a translation for Christina's Persian voicemail lady, listen to old and new songs, play a round of 'Rate My Jeans,' and much much more!
